24:48.240 --> 24:48.911
Wh-wh-wh...

24:49.040 --> 24:51.076
We could have a lot of fun together.

24:51.200 --> 24:53.873
I think we'd be really good for each other.

24:54.000 --> 24:54.955
What do you say?

24:56.800 --> 24:58.438
