before the police find it.

26:06.120 --> 26:07.075
No, no, no...

26:07.200 --> 26:09.031
- What?
- It's all right!

26:09.160 --> 26:11.116
- What?
- Ge-Ge-Ge...

26:11.240 --> 26:12.753
George...

26:12.880 --> 26:14.029
M-m-m...

26:14.160 --> 26:16.037
