26:18.160 --> 26:19.593
Yes.

26:19.760 --> 26:21.273
Where did he move it, Ken?

26:21.400 --> 26:23.038
Where did he move it?!

26:23.720 --> 26:25.676
C-c-c...

26:34.880 --> 26:38.031
I don't know where it is.
There's a key for something.

26:38.160 --> 26:39.115
It's in...

26:41.400 --> 26:42.355
Don't tell me.

26:42.480 --> 26:44.550
It's better that you don't tell me.

26:45.880 --> 26:49.395
Oh, you know, if it wasn't for George...

26:53.840 --> 26:55.319
Otto...

26:56.880 --> 26:58.632
...tried to k-k-k...

26:58.760 --> 27:00.034
...kiss me.

27:01.880 --> 27:03.438
I thought he might.

27:06.200 --> 27:07.633
No.

27:07.760 --> 27:09.716
Nothing, no marks at all.

27:09.840 --> 27:11.796
But it is a safety deposit box key?

27:11.920 --> 27:14.275
Yes, but there are millions of them...

27:14.400 --> 27:16.152
...hotels, banks, offices.

27:16.280 --> 27:17.429
Sorry.

27:17.560 --> 27:18.834
Thank you.

27:19.480 --> 27:21.152
(Fuck!)

27:36.480 --> 27:37.993
That's him.

27:38.120 --> 27:40.076
That's him, Inspector.

27:40.200 --> 27:42.714
He's the one
who tried to murder my dogs.

27:44.280 --> 27:45.952
