01:15:26.640 --> 01:15:27.959
<i>(dog yaps)</i>

01:15:53.760 --> 01:15:55.830
<i>(pulley rattles)</i>

01:16:05.480 --> 01:16:06.879
Oh, God!

01:16:42.680 --> 01:16:45.319
<i>(man)</i> Send for an ambulance!

01:17:03.880 --> 01:17:05.199
Shocking!

01:17:08.880 --> 01:17:10.438
I did it!

01:17:10.560 --> 01:17:11.959
I did it! I did it!

01:17:12.320 --> 01:17:15.073
Unbe-fuck-alievable!

01:17:15.200 --> 01:17:16.155
Thomason!

01:17:16.280 --> 01:17:17.235
Yeah?

01:17:21.280 --> 01:17:22.838
You done well, my son.

01:17:24.280 --> 01:17:25.838
Now, here's the plan.

01:17:25.960 --> 01:17:29.555
You get four tickets
for this evening for Rio, first class.

01:17:29.680 --> 01:17:31.830
- Then...
- F-f-f...

01:17:31.960 --> 01:17:33.109
Yeah, four.

01:17:33.240 --> 01:17:34.673
We get rid of Otto later.

01:17:34.800 --> 01:17:37.519
Then, back to the flat,
pack, collect me.

01:17:37.640 --> 01:17:41.110
Then to the Cathcart Towers Hotel
to pick up the jewels.

01:17:43.840 --> 01:17:48.436
Unbe-fuck-alievable!

01:17:48.560 --> 01:17:50.152
Oi! Oi!

01:17:50.280 --> 01:17:51.269
<i>(hums The Conga)</i>

01:17:53.280 --> 01:17:55.874
It's so exciting,
I can't believe it!

01:17:56.000 --> 01:17:57.035
He's s-s-safe.

01:17:57.160 --> 01:17:58.195
<i>(phone rings)</i>

01:17:58.320 --> 01:18:00.197
I'm going to be late for court!

01:18:02.280 --> 01:18:03.554
H-Hello.

01:18:03.680 --> 01:18:04.635
Hello, Otto.

01:18:06.880 --> 01:18:09.633
No, she just er... I-I-left.

01:18:10.280 --> 01:18:12.271
Oh, and Otto...

01:18:12.400 --> 01:18:14.914
You owe me a p-p-p...

01:18:16.280 --> 01:18:17.315
What?

01:18:19.080 --> 01:18:21.310
You owe me a p-p-pound.

01:18:22.880 --> 01:18:23.835
Not Granny?

01:18:24.760 --> 01:18:28.719
M-met with an accident.

01:18:29.680 --> 01:18:31.511
Bullshit! You're lying.

01:18:32.880 --> 01:18:33.835
Dead?

01:18:34.600 --> 01:18:36.158
Heart attack.

01:18:40.280 --> 01:18:41.633
I don't believe this.

01:18:41.760 --> 01:18:44.228
So, George will be out this afternoon.

01:18:44.360 --> 01:18:46.032
We all go out to Heathrow...

01:18:46.160 --> 01:18:47.718
...collect the loot and...

01:18:47.840 --> 01:18:49.239
<i>(imitates plane)</i>

01:18:49.360 --> 01:18:55.196
All thanks to me.

01:18:56.120 --> 01:18:58.714
So the loot's at the airport, is it, Ken?

01:19:08.680 --> 01:19:10.113
What's h-h-happening?

01:19:11.760 --> 01:19:12.715
Well, Ken.

01:19:13.600 --> 01:19:15.875
I'm going to ask you some questions...

01:19:16.000 --> 01:19:17.353
...while I eat my chips.

01:19:17.480 --> 01:19:18.799
First.

01:19:18.920 --> 01:19:20.512
Who was the philosopher...

01:19:20.640 --> 01:19:23.438
...who developed
the concept of the superman...

01:19:23.560 --> 01:19:25.630
...in <i>Also Spracht Zarathustra?</i>

01:19:27.480 --> 01:19:29.038
No?!

01:19:29.160 --> 01:19:31.833
That's a chip up the nose, I'm afraid.

01:19:32.840 --> 01:19:34.193
Friedrich Nietzsche.

01:19:34.320 --> 01:19:35.753
Next.

01:19:35.880 --> 01:19:38.110
In which book did Nietzsche claim...

01:19:38.240 --> 01:19:41.550
...that almost all higher culture
is based on cruelty?

01:19:43.280 --> 01:19:45.919
Are you thinking
or are you in mid-stutter?

01:19:46.040 --> 01:19:48.429
You're m-mad.

01:19:49.280 --> 01:19:51.669
<i>Beyond Good And Evil.</i>

01:19:53.280 --> 01:19:55.157
I'll have to ask you an easy one.

01:19:55.280 --> 01:19:57.077
OK. Erm...

01:19:57.200 --> 01:19:58.792
Let me think, let me think.

01:19:59.560 --> 01:20:01.232
Where are the diamonds?

01:20:02.080 --> 01:20:03.752
I'll give you a clue.

01:20:03.880 --> 01:20:06.269
Somewhere round the airport.

01:20:07.480 --> 01:20:08.833
<i>(stutters)</i>

01:20:09.080 --> 01:20:11.310
No hassle, there's plenty of time.

01:20:11.440 --> 01:20:14.830
I'll just sit here and eat my chips
till you tell me.

01:20:17.120 --> 01:20:19.839
The English contribution to world cuisine.

01:20:19.960 --> 01:20:21.678
The chip.

01:20:21.800 --> 01:20:24.633
What do the English
usually eat with chips...

01:20:24.760 --> 01:20:26.955
...to make them more interesting?

01:20:28.480 --> 01:20:30.198
Wait a moment!

01:20:32.280 --> 01:20:34.157
It's fish, isn't it?!

01:20:38.240 --> 01:20:40.037
Here, boy.

01:20:40.680 --> 01:20:43.069
Down the hatch.

01:20:46.080 --> 01:20:47.195
Delicious!

01:20:47.320 --> 01:20:49.675
You b-b-b...

01:20:49.800 --> 01:20:51.552
Better eat the green one? OK?

01:20:52.280 --> 01:20:54.555
What's this one's name?

01:20:54.680 --> 01:20:56.796
Well, not Wanda, anyway.

01:20:56.920 --> 01:20:58.592
I'm going to call her Lunch.

01:20:58.720 --> 01:21:00.790
Hello, Lunch. Hello!

01:21:05.280 --> 01:21:07.032
Eugh!

01:21:07.160 --> 01:21:09.116
Avoid the green ones.

01:21:09.240 --> 01:21:10.798
They're not ripe yet.

01:21:12.680 --> 01:21:16.878
You were in court, Inspector,
when the forensic evidence was read?

01:21:17.000 --> 01:21:17.989
Yes, sir.

01:21:18.120 --> 01:21:21.430
And the fact that Mr Thomason
was installing windows...

01:21:21.560 --> 01:21:23.232
...the previous weekend...

01:21:23.360 --> 01:21:28.957
...would explain the presence of
small particles of glass on his trousers.

01:21:30.560 --> 01:21:32.516
No hurry, Inspector.

01:21:32.640 --> 01:21:34.153
Please do take your time.

01:21:41.200 --> 01:21:42.189
I'm almost full.

01:21:44.000 --> 01:21:45.353
Almost.

01:21:45.480 --> 01:21:47.391
<i>(gasps)</i> Stop!

01:21:47.520 --> 01:21:49.431
Please, don't.

01:21:49.560 --> 01:21:50.515
Come on, Wanda!

01:21:50.640 --> 01:21:51.595
<i>(sobs)</i>

01:21:51.720 --> 01:21:52.675
Gullet time!

01:21:55.480 --> 01:21:58.597
What are the names
of those hotels by the airport?

01:21:58.720 --> 01:21:59.994
The Airway Sheraton?

01:22:00.120 --> 01:22:01.075
The Post House?

01:22:01.200 --> 01:22:02.474
The Cathcart Towers?

01:22:02.600 --> 01:22:04.556
The Cathcart Towers? Yes?

01:22:06.280 --> 01:22:07.474
Mm? Mm?

01:22:09.040 --> 01:22:10.189
Yes.

01:22:10.320 --> 01:22:11.799
In the safe deposit box?

01:22:11.920 --> 01:22:12.909
Yes.

01:22:13.040 --> 01:22:14.712
<i>(muffled)</i> Where's the key?

01:22:14.840 --> 01:22:15.795
What?

01:22:15.920 --> 01:22:16.909
Where's the key?

01:22:17.040 --> 01:22:19.031
It's in the t-t-tank.

01:22:21.000 --> 01:22:22.433
Where? Where?

01:22:22.560 --> 01:22:24.869
In the t-t-t...

01:22:25.000 --> 01:22:26.228
Treasure chest!

01:22:30.680 --> 01:22:32.511
Where?!

01:22:33.280 --> 01:22:34.315
Where?

01:22:34.440 --> 01:22:36.032
Oh!

01:22:36.680 --> 01:22:39.672
You m-m-m...

01:22:39.800 --> 01:22:43.713
...murdering k-k-k...

01:22:43.960 --> 01:22:45.712
I'll kill you, I'll kill you!

01:22:48.680 --> 01:22:52.116
Sorry, Ken,
but your answer was incorrect.

01:22:52.240 --> 01:22:55.630
Still, you really did think
it was in there, didn't you?

01:22:56.160 --> 01:22:57.639
<i>(snorts)</i>

01:22:57.760 --> 01:22:59.159
What?

01:22:59.680 --> 01:23:01.477
Oh!

01:23:08.640 --> 01:23:10.949
- Hello?
- I know where the diamonds are.

01:23:12.560 --> 01:23:13.515
Where?

01:23:13.640 --> 01:23:15.073
Where's the key?

01:23:18.560 --> 01:23:19.788
I've got it.

01:23:19.920 --> 01:23:22.309
When can you get
to George's apartment?

01:23:23.560 --> 01:23:25.551
You are Wanda Gershwitz...

01:23:25.680 --> 01:23:29.309
...of Kipling Mansions,
Murray Road, London W9?

01:23:29.440 --> 01:23:31.317
Yes.

01:23:31.440 --> 01:23:33.078
Would you tell the court...

01:23:33.200 --> 01:23:35.156
...how do you know the defendant?

01:23:35.280 --> 01:23:38.078
We've had a relationship for two years.

01:23:38.960 --> 01:23:40.552
Relationship?

01:23:40.680 --> 01:23:43.069
We're lovers, your lord.

01:23:44.520 --> 01:23:45.236
<i>(coughs)</i>

01:23:45.360 --> 01:23:48.716
Miss Gershwitz,
on 4th March of this year...

01:23:48.840 --> 01:23:50.159
...in the morning...

01:23:50.280 --> 01:23:51.315
...where were you?

01:23:51.440 --> 01:23:53.396
At the apartment at Murray Road.

01:23:53.520 --> 01:23:56.751
And were you by yourself,
or was anyone else present?

01:23:56.920 --> 01:23:59.150
No. Somebody else was there.

01:23:59.280 --> 01:24:00.713
Who was that?

01:24:00.840 --> 01:24:02.193
My brother.

01:24:02.320 --> 01:24:03.275
Did your b...?

01:24:07.480 --> 01:24:09.038
Your brother?

01:24:10.280 --> 01:24:12.111
My brother.

01:24:14.280 --> 01:24:15.554
Yes.

01:24:17.080 --> 01:24:18.479
Yes, and...

01:24:19.720 --> 01:24:22.029
Are you quite sure it was your brother?

01:24:22.160 --> 01:24:24.515
I'm sure she can recognise her brother.

01:24:24.640 --> 01:24:27.518
She's had a relationship
with him all her life.

01:24:27.640 --> 01:24:28.834
<i>(subdued laughter)</i>

01:24:29.720 --> 01:24:31.073
Much obliged, my lord.

01:24:32.200 --> 01:24:36.239
W-w-was there
anyone else present that morning?

01:24:36.360 --> 01:24:38.396
Yes, George was there.

01:24:38.520 --> 01:24:39.873
But he left about 6.55.

01:24:40.000 --> 01:24:41.592
Wanda!

01:24:41.840 --> 01:24:43.512
I-I wonder...

01:24:43.920 --> 01:24:45.717
I wonder...

01:24:47.200 --> 01:24:48.758
I wonder...

01:24:56.880 --> 01:24:58.836
Yes, Mr Leach?

01:24:59.840 --> 01:25:01.239
I Wendy... I Wanda...

01:25:01.360 --> 01:25:02.918
I wonder... I w-w-w...

01:25:03.040 --> 01:25:06.032
Wh-when you say 6.55...

01:25:06.160 --> 01:25:08.435
...Miss er... Gershwitz...

01:25:08.560 --> 01:25:11.154
...how can you be so sure?

01:25:11.280 --> 01:25:12.793
Oh, I looked at the clock.

01:25:13.120 --> 01:25:14.473
Cos I said to myself...

01:25:14.600 --> 01:25:18.195
'Where could he be going at 6.55
with that sawn-off shotgun? '

01:25:18.320 --> 01:25:19.230
Darling!

01:25:20.280 --> 01:25:21.759
Mr Leach.

01:25:21.880 --> 01:25:22.915
Darling?

01:25:23.040 --> 01:25:24.189
Yes, dear?

01:25:24.320 --> 01:25:25.275
You bitch!

01:25:25.400 --> 01:25:26.799
You fucking bitch!

01:25:26.920 --> 01:25:28.069
<i>(Wanda screams)</i>

01:25:30.920 --> 01:25:32.069
Restrain that man!

01:25:38.280 --> 01:25:39.315
Restrain this man.

01:25:39.440 --> 01:25:40.714
Come 'ere, you bastard!

01:25:40.840 --> 01:25:43.798
Clear the court!
I'm adjourning this for an hour.

01:25:43.920 --> 01:25:45.990
Clear the court!

01:25:55.240 --> 01:25:56.514
Clear the court!

01:25:56.640 --> 01:25:58.790
Clear the court! Clear the court!

01:25:58.920 --> 01:26:00.831
Officers, arrest that man!

01:26:06.680 --> 01:26:09.399
Clear the court! Clear the court!

01:26:20.160 --> 01:26:21.593
<i>(Wendy)</i> Bloody hell!

01:26:22.280 --> 01:26:24.430
It's my husband, he's been hit.

01:26:25.200 --> 01:26:26.474
Ah, you made it. Good.

01:26:26.600 --> 01:26:28.272
A bit of a knock, I'm afraid.

01:26:30.040 --> 01:26:32.952
I have never been
so humiliated in my life.

01:26:33.080 --> 01:26:36.152
You can stick this marriage
right in your bottom!

01:26:36.280 --> 01:26:37.633
I'll see you in court.

01:26:47.080 --> 01:26:48.035
Yes.

01:26:50.280 --> 01:26:51.633
Well.

01:26:52.280 --> 01:26:53.793
That's it, then.

01:26:57.280 --> 01:26:58.395
George.

01:26:58.520 --> 01:27:00.112
- What?
- We've got to talk.

01:27:00.880 --> 01:27:02.711
Tell those pigs to fuck off.

01:27:02.840 --> 01:27:04.068
Fuck off, pigs.

01:27:07.280 --> 01:27:08.759
Did you hear what I said?

01:27:08.880 --> 01:27:09.835
Fuck off.

01:27:15.040 --> 01:27:16.553
What's she up to, George?

01:27:16.680 --> 01:27:17.749
What are you up to?

01:27:18.680 --> 01:27:20.432
You called her darling...

01:27:20.560 --> 01:27:21.629
...and Wanda.

01:27:21.760 --> 01:27:24.718
I've been helping her
get her evidence straight.

01:27:24.840 --> 01:27:25.909
It slipped out.

01:27:26.040 --> 01:27:27.712
Have you been coaching her?

01:27:27.840 --> 01:27:30.354
What do you think?!
We've got ten minutes.

01:27:30.480 --> 01:27:32.436
They'll find you guilty, right?

01:27:32.560 --> 01:27:35.916
Plead guilty now, tell them
where the loot is, you may get...

01:27:36.040 --> 01:27:38.235
...eight years, out in five and a half.

01:27:38.360 --> 01:27:40.715
What if I tell them about Otto...
and Wanda?

01:27:41.280 --> 01:27:42.838
- They both did it?
- Yeah.

01:27:42.960 --> 01:27:44.029
Great, all right.

01:27:44.160 --> 01:27:45.912
Maybe six years, out in four?

01:27:46.040 --> 01:27:48.759
So where are the diamonds?

01:27:48.880 --> 01:27:50.518
Where's Bartlett?

01:27:50.640 --> 01:27:52.517
Upstairs, calming things down.

01:27:52.640 --> 01:27:53.755
So, where are they?

01:27:53.880 --> 01:27:56.474
Tell Bartlett Ken knows where they are.

01:27:57.840 --> 01:28:01.719
George, it'd be a lot quicker
if you told me.

01:28:03.880 --> 01:28:05.757
OK! I'll tell Bartlett.

01:28:05.880 --> 01:28:07.552
Where's Ken?

01:28:07.680 --> 01:28:08.874
He's at the flat.

01:28:12.280 --> 01:28:14.236
<i>(Wanda wails)</i>

01:28:14.360 --> 01:28:15.998
Thank you for all your help.

01:28:16.120 --> 01:28:17.189
I'll be right out.

01:28:31.760 --> 01:28:33.352
Taxi! Taxi!

01:28:33.480 --> 01:28:34.469
Please... shit!

01:28:34.600 --> 01:28:35.828
Taxi!

01:28:35.960 --> 01:28:37.075
Come on.

01:28:37.200 --> 01:28:38.269
- What?
- Let's go.

01:28:38.400 --> 01:28:39.833
- Where?
- Buenos Aires.

01:28:39.960 --> 01:28:42.679
- What?
- We're going to George's flat first.

01:28:42.800 --> 01:28:44.472
Get in.

01:28:47.400 --> 01:28:48.549
Got your passport?

01:28:48.680 --> 01:28:49.635
Yeah.

01:28:49.760 --> 01:28:51.796
Check the briefcase for mine.

01:28:51.920 --> 01:28:53.273
Get your head down.

01:28:58.920 --> 01:29:02.310
So, you robbed the jeweller's,
turned one lover in...

01:29:02.440 --> 01:29:05.159
...and kept one to help you
find the diamonds.

01:29:05.280 --> 01:29:07.840
When he does,
you commit perjury in court.

01:29:07.960 --> 01:29:09.712
Everyone does it in America.

01:29:09.840 --> 01:29:11.034
Not in this country!

01:29:11.160 --> 01:29:13.196
Right(!) Nobody lies in England.

01:29:13.320 --> 01:29:17.279
- Like Margaret Thatcher never lied.
- You lied to me from the start.

01:29:17.400 --> 01:29:20.915
- You just wanted to get me into bed.
- I fell in love with you!

01:29:25.480 --> 01:29:28.153
How come you dumped me, then?

01:29:28.280 --> 01:29:30.236
I wasn't rich enough, remember?

01:29:41.520 --> 01:29:43.112
Say something in Russian.

01:29:43.240 --> 01:29:44.195
No!

01:29:48.960 --> 01:29:50.791
What are you thinking, Archie?

01:29:50.920 --> 01:29:53.195
I'm trying to find one good reason...

01:29:53.320 --> 01:29:55.515
...why I should take you away with me.

01:29:55.640 --> 01:29:56.470
How about...

01:29:57.480 --> 01:30:00.552
...because I have the key
to the safety deposit box.

01:30:01.200 --> 01:30:03.395
<i>(both)</i> That's a good reason!

01:30:07.000 --> 01:30:08.433
What do we do about Otto?

01:30:08.560 --> 01:30:09.629
I'll handle Otto.

01:30:09.760 --> 01:30:11.716
Be careful, he's dangerous.

01:30:12.280 --> 01:30:13.554
So am I.

01:30:13.680 --> 01:30:15.238
Keep it running.

01:30:18.640 --> 01:30:20.756
- Why did you bring him?
- Otto, wait!

01:30:20.880 --> 01:30:23.553
- I'm beginning to think you like him!
- Wait!

01:30:23.680 --> 01:30:25.079
Let's get the diamonds!

01:30:25.320 --> 01:30:26.150
Ken!

01:30:26.280 --> 01:30:27.030
<i>(groans)</i>

01:30:27.160 --> 01:30:28.115
Are you Ken?

01:30:30.680 --> 01:30:31.635
How do you do?

01:30:31.760 --> 01:30:33.273
I'm George's barrister.

01:30:33.400 --> 01:30:35.152
<i>(brakes screech)</i>

01:30:35.280 --> 01:30:36.235
<i>(crashing)</i>

01:30:36.360 --> 01:30:37.315
Oh, my God!

01:30:37.440 --> 01:30:38.759
<i>(Otto)</i> Asshole!

01:30:38.880 --> 01:30:41.155
- What the bloody hell...
- <i>(gunshot)</i>

01:30:41.280 --> 01:30:42.838
Oh, all right, then.

01:30:44.240 --> 01:30:45.958
Archie!

01:30:47.280 --> 01:30:48.554
Where have they gone?

01:30:48.680 --> 01:30:50.432
Quick! Where have they gone?

01:30:50.560 --> 01:30:52.516
They've go... they've go...

01:30:52.640 --> 01:30:53.834
What?

01:30:53.960 --> 01:30:55.029
<i>(splutters)</i>

01:30:55.160 --> 01:30:56.229
Are you all right?

01:30:57.080 --> 01:30:58.354
Where have they gone?

01:30:58.480 --> 01:30:59.833
They've gone to the...

01:30:59.960 --> 01:31:01.075
...the Ca-ca-ca...

01:31:01.200 --> 01:31:02.679
- Are you ill?
- No, no, no.

01:31:02.800 --> 01:31:03.789
What?

01:31:03.920 --> 01:31:04.875
Ca-ca-ca...

01:31:05.000 --> 01:31:06.353
Have you got a stutter?

01:31:06.480 --> 01:31:08.596
Yeah, I have. A bit.

01:31:08.720 --> 01:31:10.153
OK, fine. Don't worry.

01:31:10.280 --> 01:31:12.157
Do you know where they've gone?

01:31:12.280 --> 01:31:13.235
Yeah.

01:31:13.360 --> 01:31:14.759
Fine, fine. Where?

01:31:14.880 --> 01:31:17.792
The Ca-ca...

01:31:17.920 --> 01:31:18.875
...Hotel.

01:31:19.600 --> 01:31:20.555
Hotel?

01:31:20.680 --> 01:31:21.635
Which hotel?

01:31:23.280 --> 01:31:24.235
Ca...

01:31:25.080 --> 01:31:27.116
The Ca... The Ca...

01:31:27.240 --> 01:31:28.639
Go on, go on.

01:31:28.760 --> 01:31:29.715
Ca-ca-ca...

01:31:29.840 --> 01:31:30.795
It's OK.

01:31:30.920 --> 01:31:33.309
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!

01:31:33.440 --> 01:31:35.396
Slowly. Very slowly.

01:31:35.520 --> 01:31:36.475
Slowly.

01:31:38.680 --> 01:31:39.999
The Ca...

01:31:41.600 --> 01:31:42.555
The Caa...

01:31:43.960 --> 01:31:44.915
The...

01:31:45.040 --> 01:31:46.598
...Ca...

01:31:46.720 --> 01:31:47.869
The Caa...

01:31:48.000 --> 01:31:48.955
No hurry.

01:31:49.080 --> 01:31:50.638
The C-C-Caaa...

01:31:50.760 --> 01:31:52.273
Sing it. Sing.

01:31:52.400 --> 01:31:53.549
<i># The Caa</i>

01:31:54.680 --> 01:31:55.908
<i># The Caa</i>

01:31:56.200 --> 01:31:57.792
<i># The Caa, the Caa</i>

01:31:59.320 --> 01:32:00.275
<i># Caa</i>

01:32:00.400 --> 01:32:01.355
Plenty of time.

01:32:01.480 --> 01:32:02.435
<i># Caa</i>

01:32:03.680 --> 01:32:04.635
<i># Caa</i>

01:32:04.760 --> 01:32:05.715
<i># The Caa</i>

01:32:05.840 --> 01:32:07.159
Oh, come on!

01:32:07.280 --> 01:32:08.713
Sorry. I'm sorry.

01:32:08.840 --> 01:32:09.795
Erm...

01:32:11.280 --> 01:32:13.032
<i># The Caa</i>

01:32:15.320 --> 01:32:16.992
Here. Write it.

01:32:28.080 --> 01:32:29.513
Cathcart Towers Hotel?

01:32:29.960 --> 01:32:31.393
Cathcart Towers Hotel.

01:32:31.520 --> 01:32:32.669
Where is it?

01:32:33.720 --> 01:32:35.233
Ken, where is it? Where?!

01:32:35.360 --> 01:32:36.588
Hea-Hea-Hea...

01:32:36.720 --> 01:32:38.153
Here. Again.

01:32:38.280 --> 01:32:39.429
No, no, no.

01:32:44.920 --> 01:32:46.990
<i>(imitates aeroplane roar)</i>

01:32:47.120 --> 01:32:48.269
Heathrow Airport.

01:32:59.000 --> 01:32:59.750
<i>(honks horn)</i>

01:32:59.880 --> 01:33:01.154
Hey! What's the idea?

01:33:01.640 --> 01:33:02.709
You can't stay...

01:33:02.840 --> 01:33:05.274
Terribly sorry. Take it, it's yours.

01:33:12.280 --> 01:33:13.349
Thank you so much.

01:33:13.480 --> 01:33:15.436
Er... British Airways to Rio.

01:33:15.560 --> 01:33:17.152
Rio? Terminal Four.

01:33:17.280 --> 01:33:18.838
Thank you.

01:33:24.160 --> 01:33:26.435
Excuse me, sir. Is this your vehicle?

01:33:26.560 --> 01:33:28.232
I'll be with you in a moment.

01:33:28.360 --> 01:33:29.509
I'll be right back.

01:33:30.440 --> 01:33:32.795
Aisle or window?
Smoking or non-smoking?

01:33:32.920 --> 01:33:34.353
What was the middle one?

01:33:34.480 --> 01:33:36.630
Anything in non-smoking, thanks.

01:33:36.760 --> 01:33:38.193
Gate 14 is boarding now.

01:34:00.720 --> 01:34:01.675
Rio!

01:34:02.680 --> 01:34:05.558
Otto, don't look back,
there's a cop behind us.

01:34:05.680 --> 01:34:06.635
Quick!

01:34:10.960 --> 01:34:12.916
Yes, we can just do it, Mr Leach.

01:34:13.040 --> 01:34:13.995
Great.

01:34:14.120 --> 01:34:15.553
- Luggage?
- <i>(thud)</i>

01:34:18.600 --> 01:34:20.192
Don't really need any.

01:34:20.320 --> 01:34:21.958
- Gate 14.
- Thank you.

01:34:23.760 --> 01:34:25.557
Ciao, stupidissimo.

01:34:32.240 --> 01:34:33.832
Ow!

01:34:34.400 --> 01:34:36.038
Aargh!

01:34:44.440 --> 01:34:47.398
<i>(gunshots)</i>

01:34:54.200 --> 01:34:56.077
Come on, Archie.

01:34:56.200 --> 01:34:57.349
Pick up the phone.

01:35:04.360 --> 01:35:06.351
Ticket, sir. Airport security.

01:35:06.480 --> 01:35:08.232
May I see your boarding pass?

01:35:08.360 --> 01:35:09.952
Oh, yes. Certainly.

01:35:10.080 --> 01:35:13.390
Very good. Would you mind
stepping over here, please?

01:35:13.520 --> 01:35:14.316
Of course.

01:35:14.440 --> 01:35:16.237
- Oh, look, the Queen.
- Where?

01:35:21.080 --> 01:35:23.036
OK, OK, OK, don't get excited.

01:35:23.160 --> 01:35:24.752
OK, OK, OK.

01:35:26.760 --> 01:35:29.752
Oh, it's you!
I was actually worried for a minute.

01:35:29.880 --> 01:35:31.552
- Keep your hands up.
- No!

01:35:31.680 --> 01:35:33.955
- Put 'em up!
- I'll make a deal with you.

01:35:34.080 --> 01:35:35.229
I'll put one up.

01:35:35.360 --> 01:35:36.839
Put the other one up!

01:35:37.680 --> 01:35:39.636
Which looks better?

01:35:40.720 --> 01:35:43.029
I'm warning you, Otto.

01:35:43.160 --> 01:35:44.593
What are you going to do?

01:35:44.760 --> 01:35:47.832
Shoot me? Gun me down in cold blood,
like a dog? Hey?

01:35:47.960 --> 01:35:51.953
If you want to settle something,
fight me. You're a man.

01:35:52.080 --> 01:35:54.036
Let's fight like men! Come on!

01:35:55.240 --> 01:35:56.753
All right.

01:35:56.880 --> 01:35:57.869
All right, then.

01:35:58.840 --> 01:36:00.717
OK. OK.

01:36:00.840 --> 01:36:02.592
You look good, Arch.

01:36:02.720 --> 01:36:04.995
That's right. I used to box for Oxford.

01:36:05.120 --> 01:36:07.554
Oh, yeah?
Well, I used to kill for the CIA.

01:36:07.680 --> 01:36:09.033
Now, get your hands up.

01:36:10.120 --> 01:36:11.075
No.

01:36:13.880 --> 01:36:16.553
<i>(laughs)</i> You spineless bimbo.

01:36:16.680 --> 01:36:18.636
Now, out.

01:36:22.520 --> 01:36:25.080
I'm going to have
to shoot you now, Archie.

01:36:25.200 --> 01:36:27.509
But I've got a little time
before my plane leaves...

01:36:27.640 --> 01:36:29.756
...and I'm longing to humiliate you.

01:36:29.880 --> 01:36:31.632
So get in that barrel.

01:36:33.480 --> 01:36:34.435
What?

01:36:34.560 --> 01:36:35.515
In the barrel.

01:36:39.680 --> 01:36:41.238
Right.

01:36:43.640 --> 01:36:44.595
You English!

01:36:44.720 --> 01:36:47.188
You think you're so superior, don't you?

01:36:47.320 --> 01:36:49.754
Well, you're the filth of the planet.

01:36:49.880 --> 01:36:52.030
- A bunch of pompous...
<i>- (chugging)</i>

01:36:52.160 --> 01:36:54.799
...badly-dressed, poverty-stricken...

01:36:54.920 --> 01:36:57.639
...sexually repressed football hooligans.

01:36:59.080 --> 01:37:00.513
Goodbye, Archie.

01:37:00.640 --> 01:37:03.029
At least we're not irretrievably vulgar.

01:37:03.160 --> 01:37:05.549
Your problem is you don't like winners.

01:37:05.680 --> 01:37:06.908
- Winners?
- Yeah.

01:37:07.040 --> 01:37:08.155
Winners.

01:37:08.280 --> 01:37:09.429
Winners like...

01:37:09.560 --> 01:37:10.675
...North Vietnam?

01:37:10.800 --> 01:37:12.074
Shut up!

01:37:12.200 --> 01:37:13.713
We did not lose Vietnam!

01:37:13.840 --> 01:37:14.989
It was a tie!

01:37:15.120 --> 01:37:18.112
I'm telling ya, baby,
they kicked a little ass there.

01:37:18.240 --> 01:37:22.552
Boy, they whupped
your hide real good!

01:37:22.680 --> 01:37:23.635
No, they didn't.

01:37:23.760 --> 01:37:25.557
- Oh, yes, they did.
- No, they didn't.

01:37:25.680 --> 01:37:27.352
Oh, yes, they did.

01:37:27.480 --> 01:37:29.038
Oh, no they...

01:37:29.160 --> 01:37:30.115
Shut up!

01:37:31.080 --> 01:37:32.149
Goodbye, Archie.

01:37:32.280 --> 01:37:33.633
Are you gonna shoot me?

01:37:33.760 --> 01:37:35.910
Er yes, I'm afraid so, old chap.

01:37:36.040 --> 01:37:37.029
Sorry!

01:37:37.160 --> 01:37:38.149
Look, Otto. Look.

01:37:45.480 --> 01:37:48.040
Revenge.

01:37:51.480 --> 01:37:52.913
It's K-K-Ken!

01:37:53.040 --> 01:37:55.838
C-c-coming to k-k-kill me.

01:37:55.960 --> 01:37:59.316
How are you going to c-c-catch me,
K-K-Ken?

01:38:01.360 --> 01:38:02.554
Now, where was I?

01:38:02.680 --> 01:38:04.033
Oh, yeah.

01:38:05.920 --> 01:38:07.672
Shit! God!

01:38:09.080 --> 01:38:11.435
Fucking limey cement!

01:38:19.640 --> 01:38:20.675
Ken! Ken!

01:38:20.800 --> 01:38:22.791
Wait, wait, Ken!

01:38:22.920 --> 01:38:25.195
Kenny! May I call you Kenny?

01:38:25.320 --> 01:38:26.309
Remember Wanda?

01:38:26.440 --> 01:38:28.032
I got the deal of a lifetime!

01:38:28.160 --> 01:38:29.559
50-50. What do you say?

01:38:29.680 --> 01:38:31.716
OK, OK, 60-40.

01:38:31.840 --> 01:38:33.193
That's my final offer.

01:38:33.320 --> 01:38:34.309
Revenge!

01:38:34.440 --> 01:38:35.589
Wait, I got an idea.

01:38:35.720 --> 01:38:37.039
You take it all.

01:38:37.160 --> 01:38:39.355
Here's my boarding pass. Ken!

01:38:39.480 --> 01:38:42.358
I'm gonna... I'm gonna k-k-kill you.

01:38:42.480 --> 01:38:43.959
OK, fine, Ken. Come at me.

01:38:44.080 --> 01:38:45.479
Give me your best shot.

01:38:45.600 --> 01:38:47.556
Go on, you don't have the guts.

01:38:47.680 --> 01:38:48.999
Admit it.

01:38:51.040 --> 01:38:52.314
OK, you have the guts.

01:38:52.440 --> 01:38:53.873
Good. Wait.

01:38:54.000 --> 01:38:55.433
Death!

01:38:55.560 --> 01:38:58.472
All right, I'm sorry
I ate your fish, OK?!

01:38:58.600 --> 01:38:59.715
I'm sorry!

01:38:59.840 --> 01:39:00.955
Revenge!

01:39:01.080 --> 01:39:02.752
Jesus, I said I'm sorry.

01:39:02.880 --> 01:39:04.791
What the fu...? Aaagh!

01:39:07.880 --> 01:39:08.756
Got him!

01:39:15.680 --> 01:39:16.635
<i>(engines roar)</i>

01:39:18.760 --> 01:39:20.716
<i>(laughs)</i> Gotcha again!

01:39:20.840 --> 01:39:22.432
You bastard!

01:39:22.880 --> 01:39:25.189
Hey! I've lost my stutter.

01:39:26.320 --> 01:39:27.469
It's gone.

01:39:27.600 --> 01:39:28.555
I can speak.

01:39:28.680 --> 01:39:31.148
How much wood could
a woodchuck chuck...

01:39:31.280 --> 01:39:33.396
...if a woodchuck could chuck wood?

01:39:33.520 --> 01:39:34.635
<i>(laughs)</i>

01:39:34.920 --> 01:39:36.035
Good afternoon, sir.

01:39:36.160 --> 01:39:37.115
Boarding pass?

01:39:37.240 --> 01:39:38.468
<i>(panting)</i>

01:39:45.080 --> 01:39:46.911
Buongiorno, signorina.

01:39:55.080 --> 01:39:56.593
Now, listen. Two things.

01:39:56.720 --> 01:39:58.233
One.

01:39:58.360 --> 01:40:01.875
Behave yourself from now on,
or I'll break your neck, OK.

01:40:03.160 --> 01:40:04.115
Two.

01:40:05.520 --> 01:40:06.475
Gorbachov.

01:40:07.080 --> 01:40:08.035
Glasnost.

01:40:08.680 --> 01:40:09.795
Molotov.

01:40:11.280 --> 01:40:12.235
Blinis.

01:40:13.280 --> 01:40:15.510
Er... Lenin.

01:40:15.640 --> 01:40:17.756
<i>(Archie)</i> Pushkin.

01:40:17.880 --> 01:40:19.029
Chicken Kiev.

01:40:19.160 --> 01:40:21.435
Good. Dostoevsky.

01:40:21.560 --> 01:40:23.073
Roubles.

01:40:25.560 --> 01:40:27.152
<i>Vladivostok.</i>

01:40:27.280 --> 01:40:28.952
<i>(engines roar)</i>

01:40:31.680 --> 01:40:36.959
Assho-o-ole!

